'''Livano Shyron Liomar Comenencia''' (born 3 February 2004) is a professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[right-back]] for [[Swiss Super League]] club [[FC Zürich|Zürich]].<ref>{{Soccerway|livano-comenencia/696780|accessdate=4 October 2021}}</ref> Born in the Netherlands, he plays for the [[Curaçao national football team|Curaçao national team]].

==Club career==
Comenencia joined the youth academy of [[PSV Eindhoven|PSV]] in 2012, and was promoted to their reserves in 2021.<ref>{{Cite web| last = Elfrink| first = Rik| title = Talentvolle Livano Comenencia (18) tekent na meer dan een half leven bij PSV bij tot 2025| work = [[Eindhovens Dagblad]]| access-date = 20 November 2023| date = 11 February 2022| url = https://www.ed.nl/psv/talentvolle-livano-comenencia-18-tekent-na-meer-dan-een-half-leven-bij-psv-bij-tot-2025~a2f5d4b5/| language = nl}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web| title = Onvergetelijke dag voor PSV-talent: 'Mijn ouders moesten bijna huilen'| work = Voetbal International| access-date = 20 November 2023| date = 11 February 2022| url = https://www.vi.nl/nieuws/onvergetelijke-dag-voor-psv-talent-mijn-ouders-moesten-bijna-huilen| language = nl}}</ref> On 13 February 2022, he signed a professional contract with PSV until 2025.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.psv.nl/english-psv/news/article/18-year-old-livano-comenencia-signs-new-deal-until-2025.htm|title=18-year-old Livano Comenencia signs new deal until 2025|date=13 February 2022|website=www.psv.nl}}</ref>

In 2021, he was included in ''[[The Guardian]]''<nowiki/>'s yearly list of the 60 best talents born in 2004 in world football.<ref name="TGuard2">{{Cite news |last1=Christenson |first1=Marcus |last2=Bandini |first2=Nicky |title=Next Generation 2021: 60 of the best young talents in world football |language=en-GB |work=[[The Guardian]] |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/ng-interactive/2021/oct/07/next-generation-2021-60-of-the-best-young-talents-in-world-football |access-date=1 September 2022 |issn=0261-3077}}</ref>

On 31 August 2023, Comenencia joined Italian side [[Juventus Next Gen]], the [[reserve team]] of [[Juventus FC|Juventus]], for an undisclosed fee, signing a two-year contract with the [[Serie C]] club.<ref>{{Cite web |date=31 August 2023 |title=Livano Comenencia è bianconero |url=https://www.juventus.com/it/news/articoli/juventus-next-gen-livano-comenencia-e-bianconero |access-date=1 September 2023 |website=Juventus.com |language=it-IT}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=1 September 2023 |title=Juve, c'è l'annuncio di Comenencia: i dettagli dell'operazione |url=https://corrieredellosport.it/news/calcio/calcio-mercato/juventus/2023/09/01-112473230/juve_c_e_l_annuncio_di_comenencia_i_dettagli_dell_operazione |access-date=1 September 2023 |website=Corriere dello Sport |language=it-IT}}</ref>

On 6 August 2025, Comenencia signed a four-season contract with [[Swiss Super League]] club [[FC Zürich|Zürich]] in Switzerland.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=FC Zürich|url=https://www.fcz.ch/pages/news/livano-comenencia-wechselt-zum-fc-zurich|title=Livano Comenencia wechselt zum FC Zürich|trans-title=Livano Comenencia moves to FC Zurich|date=6 August 2025|access-date=7 August 2025|language=de}}</ref>

==International career==
Born in the Netherlands, Comenencia is of Curaçaoan descent.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.sport.de/fussball/pe562471/livano-comenencia/|title=Livano Comenencia|website=sport.de}}</ref> He was a youth international for the Netherlands, having played with them up to the [[Netherlands national under-18 football team|Netherlands U18]]s.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.vi.nl/cookies/;jsessionid=E54545011E9C27ECFA5256E29D04DA5A|title=Privacyinstellingen op VI.nl|website=vi.nl}}</ref>

In October 2024, he accepted a senior call-up from the [[Curaçao national football team]] for the games against [[Grenada national football team|Grenada]] of the [[2024–25 CONCACAF Nations League]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/DA0Scn-uuzV/ |publisher=Curaçao national football team – Official Instagram |title=🚨UPDATE: Comenencia joins the Blue Wave |accessdate=10 October 2024 |date=7 October 2024 }}</ref>

